2025-11-06PPCFree Trade and Labour Mobility in Canada ActFree Trade and Labour Mobility in Canada RegulationsFree Trade and Labour Mobility in Canada Regulations in order to (1) provide exceptions to the application of the Act in the areas of supply-management and safety of food; (2) impose conditions and restrictions for the application of the Act’s provisions on goods, services and labour mobility; and (3) provide further clarification of certain key terms in the Act.Registration: SOR/2025-0225 Publication Date: 2025-11-19
act: Free Trade and Labour Mobility in Canada Act
subject: Free Trade and Labour Mobility in Canada Regulations
precis: Free Trade and Labour Mobility in Canada Regulations in order to (1) provide exceptions to the application of the Act in the areas of supply-management and safety of food; (2) impose conditions and restrictions for the application of the Act’s provisions on goods, services and labour mobility; and (3) provide further clarification of certain key terms in the Act.
